review: Very friendly and experienced Doctor. The explanation of my health issue was very professional, all in all, I was very happy and satisfied with my consultation.
*** ** *** **** ******* * **** ***** ** *******explained all the procedure before hand only with so much clarity....less waiting time.....n top class treatment....i recommend him to all my friends.

One of the coolest doctor with tonnes of patience and he carries the cute smile till the end.one good thing about Vinay is he makes you  feel comfortable with your negetives and gives very good examples to overcome.
